.Sh SIGNAL HANDLER SAFETY
The server's
.Va running
flag is declared as
.Vt volatile sig_atomic_t
to ensure safe access from signal handler context.
This prevents undefined behaviour when
.Fn handle_signal
writes to the flag during asynchronous signal delivery.
